  ('0fe5b823-a9ab-541c-90bb-e42f75d664d9', 'AGR_RF_COMP_01', 'IND_AGR_D07', 'AGR_RF_COMP_01_DR01', 'Export Documentation Support operates in Produce Aggregation, Post-Harvest Handling and Market Linkage within Agriculture, Forestry & Fishing, where the workplace setting involves farm, crop, livestock, fisheries, forestry, procurement, quality, field advisory, and agri-value-chain execution. It handles inputs and evidence such as field/farm checklist; crop or livestock observation log; procurement/quality note; extension visit record; agri-operation handoff. Day to day, the role checks role-specific inputs, notices missing details or exceptions, updates trackers or review files, prepares handoff evidence, and escalates unresolved issues. The role handles routine checks, evidence preparation, and handoff within Produce Aggregation, Post-Harvest Handling and Market Linkage; it escalates exceptions requiring senior judgement, formal approval, regulated sign-off, or authority beyond its role boundary. Output proof for this role includes field/farm checklist; crop or livestock observation log; procurement/quality note; extension visit record; agri-operation handoff. Its role-environment RIASEC alignment is CSE (Conventional / Social / Enterprising), reflecting structured records, process control, compliance, documentation, scheduling, or accuracy-focused work; service, support, teaching, guidance, guest/user interaction, or community coordination; influence, ownership, persuasion, stakeholder leadership, commercial decision support, or program responsibility.', 'C', 'S', 'E', 'CSE', 'Export Documentation Support is mapped to CSE because its Agriculture / Farm Operations / Agri-Value Chain environment involves farm, crop, livestock, forestry, fisheries, procurement, quality, field advisory, and agri-value-chain execution. Conventional / Social / Enterprising is relevant because the role uses structured records, process control, compliance, documentation, scheduling, or accuracy-focused work; service, support, teaching, guidance, guest/user interaction, or community coordination; influence, ownership, persuasion, stakeholder leadership, commercial decision support, or program responsibility while producing evidence such as farm/field checklist, livestock/crop observation log, procurement/quality note, extension visit record, and agri-operation handoff.', 'Checks field/farm checklist; crop or livestock observation log; procurement/quality note; extension visit record; agri-operation handoff against the current Produce Aggregation, Post-Harvest Handling and Market Linkage requirement; notices missing fields, mismatched values, timing gaps, quality exceptions, or unresolved handoff items; updates the relevant tracker, checklist, issue note, review file, or handoff record; proves the behaviour through field/farm checklist; crop or livestock observation log; procurement/quality note; extension visit record; agri-operation handoff.', 'Export Documentation Support works in Produce Aggregation, Post-Harvest Handling and Market Linkage within Agriculture, Forestry & Fishing. The role context is farm, crop, livestock, fisheries, forestry, procurement, quality, field advisory, and agri-value-chain execution; its work is evidenced through field/farm checklist; crop or livestock observation log; procurement/quality note; extension visit record; agri-operation handoff.', 'Export Documentation Support: checks farm, crop, livestock, fisheries, forestry, procurement, quality, field advisory, and agri-value-chain execution; reviews role inputs and exceptions in Produce Aggregation, Post-Harvest Handling and Market Linkage; updates the relevant tracker or checklist; prepares field/farm checklist; crop or livestock observation log; procurement/quality note; extension visit record; agri-operation handoff; escalates items needing senior approval, regulated sign-off, or cross-team decision authority.', 'Export Documentation Support output evidence includes: Export Documentation Support field/farm observation sheet with location, crop/livestock/input condition, and action required; Export Documentation Support production/procurement/quality tracker with quantity, grade, issue, and handoff status; Export Documentation Support advisory or inspection note documenting farmer/site interaction, finding, and escalation; Export Documentation Support agri-operation evidence pack with dated photos/records, checklist, and reviewer sign-off.', '{"numerical_reasoning": 53.0, "logical_reasoning": 69.0, "verbal_reasoning": 88.0, "spatial_reasoning": 36.0, "data_interpretation": 55.0, "pattern_recognition": 52.0}'::jsonb, '{"openness": 3.0, "extraversion": 5.0, "agreeableness": 3.0, "conscientiousness": 5.0, "emotional_stability": 4.0}'::jsonb, '{"impact": 3.0, "status": 4.0, "autonomy": 3.0, "security": 3.0, "financial": 4.0, "lifestyle": 2.0, "creativity": 2.0, "leadership": 4.0}'::jsonb, '{"areas": ["Verbal Reasoning", "Logical Reasoning", "Data Interpretation"], "rationale": "Export Documentation Support depends most on verbal reasoning, logical reasoning, data interpretation because the work involves client interaction, persuasion, need discovery, objection handling, and commercial follow-up. Lower readiness in the mandatory areas should trigger bridge practice rather than automatic rejection unless the role is safety, license, or authority gated."}'::jsonb, '{"traits": ["Conscientiousness", "Extraversion", "Emotional Stability"], "rationale": "Export Documentation Support benefits from conscientiousness, extraversion, emotional stability because the role requires client interaction, persuasion, need discovery, objection handling, and commercial follow-up. These traits should adjust confidence and coaching focus, not act as a hard exclusion rule."}'::jsonb, '{"values": ["Financial Growth", "Leadership", "Status"], "rationale": "Export Documentation Support aligns best with learners who value financial growth, leadership, status because the role environment involves client interaction, persuasion, need discovery, objection handling, and commercial follow-up. Work values should be used to prioritise role options, not to prove technical ability."}'::jsonb, 'Preferred', 'B.Sc Agriculture; Veterinary; Fisheries; Forestry; Dairy; Agri Engineering; Rural Management; Any degree with agri-field exposure', true),
