movement point; Therapist guest exception note with complaint, safety/service signal, response, and escalation owner; Therapist shift or trip handover sheet with completed actions, pending requests, and feedback proof.', '{"numerical_reasoning": 66.0, "logical_reasoning": 82.0, "verbal_reasoning": 58.0, "spatial_reasoning": 86.0, "data_interpretation": 63.0, "pattern_recognition": 69.0}'::jsonb, '{"openness": 3.0, "extraversion": 3.0, "agreeableness": 3.0, "conscientiousness": 5.0, "emotional_stability": 4.0}'::jsonb, '{"impact": 4.0, "status": 3.0, "autonomy": 2.0, "security": 3.0, "financial": 4.0, "lifestyle": 2.0, "creativity": 2.0, "leadership": 3.0}'::jsonb, '{"areas": ["Spatial Reasoning", "Logical Reasoning", "Pattern Recognition"], "rationale": "Therapist depends most on spatial reasoning, logical reasoning, pattern recognition because the work involves field execution, technical checking, safety awareness, practical problem solving, and structured site follow-up. Lower readiness in the mandatory areas should trigger bridge practice rather than automatic rejection unless the role is safety, license, or authority gated."}'::jsonb, '{"traits": ["Conscientiousness", "Emotional Stability", "Agreeableness"], "rationale": "Therapist benefits from conscientiousness, emotional stability, agreeableness because the role requires field execution, technical checking, safety awareness, practical problem solving, and structured site follow-up. These traits should adjust confidence and coaching focus, not act as a hard exclusion rule."}'::jsonb, '{"values": ["Financial Growth", "Impact", "Leadership"], "rationale": "Therapist aligns best with learners who value financial growth, impact, leadership because the role environment involves field execution, technical checking, safety awareness, practical problem solving, and structured site follow-up. Work values should be used to prioritise role options, not to prove technical ability."}'::jsonb, 'Mandatory', 'Hospitality; Tourism; BBA; Event Management; Any degree with customer-service or operations portfolio', true)
) AS v(ctx_id, fam_code, dom_code, role_code, c0, c1, c2, c3, c4, c5, c6, c7, c8, c9, c10, c11, c12, c13, c14, c15, c16, c17, c18)
JOIN public.role r ON r.code = v.role_code
JOIN public.role_families rf ON rf.code = v.fam_code
JOIN public.domains d ON d.code = v.dom_code
JOIN public.industry_domains idm ON idm.domain_id = d.id
JOIN public.role_family_domains rfd ON rfd.role_family_id = rf.id AND rfd.industry_domain_id = idm.id
ON CONFLICT (id) DO UPDATE SET
  description = EXCLUDED.description, degree_gate = EXCLUDED.degree_gate,
  is_active = EXCLUDED.is_active, updated_at = now();
